Links a schema revision to a specific name.
Tagging a schema is considered to be an update as well.
PUT /v1/schemas/{org_label}/{project_label}/{schema_id}/tags?rev={previous_rev}
  {
    "tag": "{name}",
    "rev": {rev}
  }
… where
{previous_rev}: Number - is the last known revision for the resolver. {name}: String - label given to the schemas at specific revision. {rev}: Number - the revision to link the provided {name}.
